Install
----------

::

	pip install pysabertooth

Usage
--------

.. code-block:: python

	from pysabertooth import Sabertooth

	saber = Sabertooth('/dev/tty.usbserial', baudrate=115200, address=128, timeout=0.1)

	# drive(number, speed)
	# number: 1-2
	# speed: -100 - 100
	saber.drive(1, 50)
	saber.drive(2, -75)
	saber.stop()


